<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>{{ subject }}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; max-width: 560px; margin: 32px auto; padding: 24px; color: #1a1a2e;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 28px; margin: 0 0 12px;">Welcome to Drivly, {{ name }}.</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 16px;">
    You're in. Browse 350,000+ cars across 10,000+ cities, book in a click, and skip the rental counter for good.
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 24px;">
    Want to make money on your idle car? You can list yours in about ten minutes — average host earnings are $10,516/year.
  </p>
  <a href="https://drivly.localhost/search"
     style="display: inline-block; background: #FF3E54; color: #fff; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
    Find a car
  </a>
  <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6c757d; margin: 32px 0 0;">
    You're getting this because you signed up at drivly.localhost with {{ email }}.
  </p>
</body>
</html>
